        p Go from zero dance experience to dancing with confidence in 14-days with this step-by-step accelerator for newer dancers!

    .class
      .class-item
        img(src="https://source.unsplash.com/200x200/?Spanish-Dance,Dance", alt="photos")
        h2 Shuffle Masterclass
